In re PALEAIS. (Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. February 9, 1923.) No. 152. J. G. M. Browne and Barnett E. Kopelman, both of New York City, for petitioner. David B. Tolins and Max Silverstein, both of New York City, for respondent.

Before HOUGH, MANTON, and MAYER, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Petition dismissed in open court.
